sub_title: Research master's student in Sociology and Social Research
summary: Currently studying at Utrecht University and working on my thesis about the retirement preparation of the solo self-employed workers. So far, I have been learning quantitative research methodology. I am interested in many different research topics and approaches - most importantly, I am trying to understand myself!
